label.value: objective specification

definition.value: A directive information entity that describes an intended process endpoint. When part of a plan specification the concretization is realized in a planned process in which the bearer tries to effect the world so that the process endpoint is achieved.

label.value: action specification

definition.value: A directive information entity that describes an action the bearer will take.

label.value: data item

definition.value: An information content entity that is intended to be a truthful statement about something (modulo, e.g., measurement precision or other systematic errors) and is constructed/acquired by a method which reliably tends to produce (approximately) truthful statements.

label.value: information content entity

label.value: directive information entity
